 <instruction>wenn es sey gepraten So . lass chalten</instruction>
 So <instruction>nym <ingredient en="bread crust" commodity="Q990859">rintten von prat</ingredient> <ingredient en="pepper" commodity="Q3143131">pheffer</ingredient> . <ingredient en="ginger" commodity="Q15046077">Ingwer</ingredient> <ingredient en="caraway" commodity="Q22978145">Kuemb</ingredient> <ingredient en="vinegar" commodity="Q41354">essech</ingredient> vnd mal das zusamen</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>erwell es . das eben dikch werd</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>leg es In das <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">Condiment</dish></instruction>
 <kitchenTip>Im selben <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">Condinent</dish> pehalt <alternative reason="ingredient">dem <ingredient en="venison" commodity="Q2296872">hiersein</ingredient> sein <dish en="roast" commodity="Q899561">pratten</dish> vnd auch den gepratten <ingredient en="rabbit" commodity="Q3556748">hasen</ingredient></alternative></kitchenTip> <closer>gib es hin</closer> </div></body></text></TEI>